WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.020 --> 00:00:02.020
Oh, God, God!

2
00:00:02.020 --> 00:00:04.019
What do you think you're doing?

3
00:00:04.019 --> 00:00:06.019
She's playing my role.

4
00:00:08.019 --> 00:00:13.019
Carla, what the hell was that that wasn't even in the script?

5
00:00:13.019 --> 00:00:15.019
I was just adding some extra touch to it.

6
00:00:15.019 --> 00:00:16.019
You know?

7
00:00:16.019 --> 00:00:17.019
The sake of art.

8
00:00:17.019 --> 00:00:18.019
Art?

9
00:00:18.019 --> 00:00:21.019
The slap doesn't make any sense.

10
00:00:21.019 --> 00:00:25.019
Who gave you the authority to change my script?

11
00:00:25.019 --> 00:00:26.019
It's fine.

12
00:00:26.019 --> 00:00:28.140
She can hit me.

13
00:00:28.140 --> 00:00:30.879
Velma, are you sure about this?

14
00:00:30.879 --> 00:00:33.880
It's all good if it's all for the sake of the effect.

15
00:00:33.880 --> 00:00:39.060
I knew I was right. I'm choosing you as my name.

16
00:00:39.060 --> 00:00:42.479
Okay, okay. Back to one, please.

17
00:00:42.479 --> 00:00:44.479
Yes, thank you. Keep it in my script.

18
00:00:44.479 --> 00:00:47.700
And action.

19
00:00:47.700 --> 00:00:49.700
You have to leave now.

20
00:00:49.700 --> 00:00:51.700
Not without the love of my life.

21
00:00:51.700 --> 00:00:53.700
I'll wait for him no matter what.

22
00:00:53.700 --> 00:01:02.820
Edward, good to see you here.

23
00:01:02.820 --> 00:01:04.819
Were you watching me?

24
00:01:04.819 --> 00:01:07.819
Me and Velma make a perfecty no way.

25
00:01:07.819 --> 00:01:09.819
Jay, have these two switch roles.

26
00:01:09.819 --> 00:01:13.689
I want Velma to do the slapping,

27
00:01:13.689 --> 00:01:15.689
since it's all for the sake of art.

